SUMMARY:Beanblossom Bottoms 30th Anniversary: Advanced Wetland Botany with
  Kevin Tungesvick
DTSTART:20260712T100000
DTEND:20260712T120000
UID:ac2c98ead15e6fe11060895c2ba69e96@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Dive deep into the diverse plant life of Beanblossom Bottoms w
 ith this advanced botany class. Explore wetland ecosystems\, identify key 
 species\, and discuss their ecological roles with Kevin\, a lifelong botan
 ist and current ecologist with Eco Logic LLC. Perfect for seasoned plant e
 nthusiasts and professionals. Bring a field notebook and waterproof boots!
  Kevin is a Restoration Ecologist with Eco Logic\, and worked as a botanis
 t for Spence Restoration Nursery. This event was rescheduled from June 14 
 due to spring flooding. If this hike is full\, sign up for the wait list h
 ere.
LOCATION:Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Preserve
