UID:cd7a763abece8903c6f0a09fcf378495@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Join Education Director Saige Sentell for a 2.5-mile guided hi
 ke at Porter West Preserve. We&#8217\;ll explore the preserve&#8217\;s bea
 utiful and diverse habitats on moderate to rugged terrain\, taking time to
  learn about the native plants\, trees\, birds\, and anything else we disc
 over along the way. This is a casual\, exploration hike where everyone is 
 encouraged to share their interests and knowledge\, or to listen and enjoy
  the hike. Bring your favorite field guides\, binoculars\, and curiosity!
